  "text": "Using specific lipid degradation products from 5 -sterols and monounsaturated fatty acids that have been proposed for distinguishing biotic from abiotic processes, and photooxidation from autoxidation [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] , we evaluated the roles played by heterotrophic, photodegradative, and autoxidative processes in the degradation of the main components of OM (higher plants, micro-algae and bacteria).",
